        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> On a dot like Splurt that does 1600 points over 96 seconds, what will the total damage done? Considering a dot like Splurt works on a scale, starting out with 1 point of damage, and increases drastically each tick, if it's extended 15%, will the rate of damage continue at that point, or? Just curious. Thanks!</P><P> </font></td>

